### Copy a Package

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/apps/[guid]/packages?source_package_guid=[guid]" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :copy_of_packages, '/v3/packages' %>
```

This endpoint copies the bits of a source package to a target package.

#### Definition
`POST /v3/apps/:guid/packages`

#### Required Query Parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
**source_package_guid** | _uuid_ | Source of package to copy from.

